# Data Cleaning and Preprocessing using Python

## Objective
Clean and preprocess a raw dataset using Python (Pandas).

## Dataset
Customer Personality Analysis (Kaggle)

## Tools Used
- Python
- Pandas
- VS Code

## Data Cleaning Steps
- Loaded the dataset
- Checked missing values
- Removed duplicate rows
- Standardized text values
- Renamed column headers
- Verified data types
- Saved the cleaned dataset

## Files
- task1.py
- cleaned_dataset.csv
- Data_Cleaning_Report.pdf

## Skills Learned
- Data Cleaning
- Data Preprocessing
- Pandas
- Handling Missing Values
- Removing Duplicates
